Package: ineAtlas
Title: Access to Spanish Income Distribution Atlas Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Pablo", "García Guzmán", , "garciagp@ebrd.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4642-7400"))
Description: Provides tools to access data from the Spanish Statistical 
    Office's Atlas de Distribución de Renta de los Hogares (Income Distribution Atlas). 
    The package offers functions to fetch standardized socioeconomic indicators at multiple 
    geographic levels (municipality, district, and census tract), including income metrics, 
    demographic characteristics, and inequality measures.
